Package: S3
Title: Helpers for Programming with the S3 Object System
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: c(
    person("Hadley", "Wickham", , "hadley@rstudio.com", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("RStudio", role = "cph")
  )
Description: S3 is a very flexible system which can lead to frustration. 
    This packages provides helpers to support a system of using S3 that
    trades freedom for ease of use. It also provides constructors and other
    helpers for important S3 classes in base R.
License: GPL-3
Imports:
